title: Ebro In The Morning - New Music Monday  + Fugees World Tour Cancelled
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 1/24/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez, and the crew are in the studio - Ebro brings up Big Energy once again while discussing Shansea and Meg Thee Stallion's new single "Lick (47)!" The crew discusses their wild weekends, OBJ played himself, and the gurus give advice! All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
